name: Mask of Duality
description:
Some time in the future, an advanced telescope designed after an iconic window shape will detect an anomaly in space. Exposed to a naked singularity, an interdimensional rift reveal to the observer the likeness of an alien mask, which then vanishes back to its origin, many parsecs away.

My tribute to John Karel's iconic windows series.
